# Licensing

Copyright (c) 2026 Smart Squad S.r.l. (https://smartsquad.io)

This repository contains two parts under two different licenses. Each
directory ships its own `LICENSE` file with the full, authoritative terms.

## Open engine — MIT

- `packages/scanner`
- `apps/cli`

The audit engine and the command-line interface are open source under the
MIT License. See [`packages/scanner/LICENSE`](./packages/scanner/LICENSE) and
[`apps/cli/LICENSE`](./apps/cli/LICENSE).

## Dashboard — PolyForm Shield 1.0.0 (source-available, no-compete)

- `apps/web`
- `packages/supabase`

The hosted dashboard and its Supabase layer are © Smart Squad S.r.l. and are
made available under the PolyForm Shield License 1.0.0 — source-available, but
not open source: you may not use them to provide a product that competes with
isready.ai. See [`apps/web/LICENSE`](./apps/web/LICENSE) and
[`packages/supabase/LICENSE`](./packages/supabase/LICENSE), and the root
[`NOTICE`](./NOTICE).

When in doubt about which terms apply to a given file, the `LICENSE` in the
nearest parent directory governs.

## Changes to licensing

Smart Squad S.r.l. reserves the right, at its sole discretion and to the extent
permitted by applicable law, to change the terms under which it makes future
versions of isready.ai available — including moving components between the open
(MIT) and source-available (PolyForm Shield) parts, or adopting different
license terms. Any such change applies only from the version in which it is
introduced onward: copies and versions already released under a given license
remain governed by the license that applied to them at the time of their
release and are not retroactively revoked.
